# Pricing and ROI Rules

Pricing must be deterministic.

Do not use AI to calculate:
- refurbishment costs
- VAT
- contingency
- ROI
- profit
- investment score
- gross yield

Use pricing engine for estimates:
src/core/pricing/pricingEngine.ts

Use ROI engine for investment metrics:
src/core/roi/roiEngine.ts

VAT:
- default 20%

Contingency:
- default 10%

ROI formula:
estimated_profit = estimated_gdv - total_project_cost
roi = estimated_profit / total_project_cost * 100

All pages must consume shared engines instead of duplicating formulas.
